    SHORT="HexCalc is a simple calculator similar to GNOME calculator."
LONG="
HexCalc is a simple calculator similar to GNOME calculator. It can do
calculations in hexadecimal, octal, binary, and non-floating point decimal.
It uses a 32bit signed integer. It is a helpful little coder utility. 
